Lucide is a plugin-based document viewer.

Included plugins:

   Supported file type         Supported features
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------
         PDF                   Scaling, Navigation, Text selection,
                               Searching, Asynchronous rendering
                               
         DJVU                  Scaling
         
         JPG                   -
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------

!!! DJVU plugin require LIBC: 
    ftp://ftp.netlabs.org/pub/gcc/libc-0.6.1-csd1.zip

Current limitations:
 
 - Printing not implemented
 - Some menuitems doesn't work
 
-- 
